com.ibm.di.parser

Class IdMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.di.parser.ParserImpl
      • com.ibm.di.parser.xml.XMLParser2
        • com.ibm.di.parser.IdMLParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParserInterface, VersionInfoInterface

    public class IdMLParser
extends XMLParser2
    The Parser used to parse IdML XML documents (or books). It is designed only for reading IdML files. For more information how they can be written, see OpenIdMLFC, CloseIdMLFC, RollingIdMLFC and IdMLConnector.
    Since:
    7.1
